{{Rumor of the Ten-Thousand-Year Sakura|Infobox}}

{{Description
| en = The rumor that four girls went to her place where they awaited the blooming of cherry blossoms. With the adjustment to her content and the introduction of modern technologies, now she can also go out for activities, despite that she can be regarded as a weirdo lacking common sense. She has always longing to go back to the one who loves mountains.
| jp = ４人の少女が自分の所に訪れて、満開の花を咲かせることを待ち望んでいたウワサ。現在は内容の調整と現代技術の応用によって外でも活動しているが、常識が欠けており特異な人物として見られている。いつも山か大好きな人の所に帰りたい。
}}

